# Firebase Configuration for StudentHub NG
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your Firebase credentials

# Get these from Firebase Console > Project Settings > Your Apps > Web App

# IMPORTANT: The DATABASE_URL must include the full URL with https://
# Example: https://studenthub-ng-default-rtdb.firebaseio.com

# After filling in the values, rename this file to .env
# Do NOT commit the .env file to git (it's in .gitignore
